---
title: Sheet Pan Chicken & Poblano Fajitas with Pico de Gallo, Monterey Jack & Lime Crema
description: Tonight’s meal is quick, easy, and downright delicious. It’s got it all—we’re talking spiced chicken, strips of poblano, and sliced onion, all tossed on a baking sheet and roasted until tender and lightly charred. The joyous jumble is then piled into steamy flour tortillas along with fresh salsa, a drizzle of lime crema, and a sprinkle of Monterey Jack cheese. Talk about a fiesta on your plate!
